{"tid":1596871,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我係林鄭今日對話完就會笑呵呵","createTime":"2019-09-26T16:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:57:28.000Z","uid":226819,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b78c4121afc261c3afce0ba3d97743dbf62d9dce","tid":1596871,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"扮到一副虛心聆聽既樣，然後友你班友仔up，然後一直講自己野，等中立派較愚蠢既人會覺得政府真係聽緊。<br />\n<br />\n然後你班深黃一直反對警暴，我係林鄭真的笑到見牙唔見眼，明明問題出現於<span style=\"color: green;\">制度裡面</span>，結果果果睇表面，警暴KO左又點？普通話，150個.....好多好多野都依然可以整死香港，結果一班人提警察冰山一角既事件而忽略左制度暴力....<br />\n<br />\n我同大家講！！ <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選，港人治港</span></span>先可以深層解決問題！"},{"pid":"41ddfdbea0cc0c8ff9e445e9625f9d054e15126b","tid":1596871,"uid":226819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:45:41.000Z","msg":"donald trump 都話要自治,<strong> autonomy</strong>!"},{"pid":"d2a9bf5ed2ec5dac8e76b832e0f5934e05427012","tid":1596871,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad2742dad28c10368821d7059ae1645bc366bb0d","tid":1596871,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89e4448d1d10ebbd1c2806494f3123e3953fdb9f","tid":1596871,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f29376b8758fd8361a7ac38696c1359704958e27","tid":1596871,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"pudh"},{"pid":"111f8530dc0be6682a9025e4aaf059457dfb1a93","tid":1596871,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"有個平台去勸你地班深黃<br />\n<br />\n但佢就企硬<br />\n<br />\n好撚work"},{"pid":"0815